Introduction

MAKAMAKA (also sometimes written as 'Maka`Maka and MAKA` MAKA) is a five-member girl group under BLUEMOON Entertainment. They debuted on August 4, 2020, with their first single "Burning Power".

The group’s name means “friendly friend”.
